Lead JavaScript Developer - React TypeScript

Posted about 10 hours ago
2314

London, England, £70000 - £95000 per annum + benefits

Job Type: Permanent

Managed by: Front End Web Team

Lead JavaScript Developer (Front End JavaScript React Redux TypeScript) *Remote Interview WFH*. Are you a senior JavaScript Developer who wants to remain hands-on and take a lead role? You could be joining a well funded technology scale-up and working on extremely complex geolocation systems that allow users to pinpoint locations anywhere on the globe with outstanding levels of accuracy; it's used by a diverse range of clients from the automotive sector to emergency services and UNICEF.

As a Lead JavaScript Developer you will create consumer facing products that are used by millions every day across maps, the corporate site as well as the developer portal and playground. You will partner with product and UX teams, receiving and inputting on designs and feasibility checks and bringing fresh ideas to continually improve on the core product. The company has technology and innovation at its core; the tech stack is built on a massively scalable microservices architecture based around Kubernetes on AWS.

As a senior member of the team you'll partner with the CTO to plan budgets and make the technology decisions as well as provide technical leadership to a small team.

There's currently a remote interview and onboarding process with full time work from home until the end of the year, thereafter you will be in the office around three days a week (with the rest of the week WFH) as part of a friendly, diverse, international team with weekly lunch and learning sessions.

Requirements:
*You have strong commercial experience as a Front End Developer with all of the following: JavaScript, React, Redux and TypeScript
*You have experience of building user interfaces on top of RESTful APIs
*You're experienced with building responsive sites for desktop, tablet and mobile
*You're collaborative with good communication skills, keen to be part of a diverse and creative team
*You're degree educated in a STEM subject

As a Lead JavaScript Developer you will earn a competitive salary (to £85k) plus benefits including 25 days holiday, share options, Pension, private medical care with BUPA and Life Assurance as well as perks such as birthday vouchers and socials.

Apply now or call to find out more about this Lead JavaScript Developer (JavaScript React Redux TypeScript) opportunity.
